    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "text_fresh",
      "x": 293.2426233685426,
      "y": 818.17814023802,
      "width": 325,
      "height": 294,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#3b0764",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772874926179,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "setup.sh  —  Fresh Install\n──────────────────────────────────\nexport OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...\nexport DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-...\nexport LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET=...\n\n./setup.sh --email you@email.com\n\nScript steps:\n 1. DNS check (EC2 IP vs domain)\n 2. Validate API keys\n 3. Install: python3 pip3 node npm\n 4. Install: nginx certbot graphviz\n 5. pip install -r requirements.txt\n 6. npm install && npm run build\n 7. Write backend/.env (mode 600)\n 8. Issue SSL cert via certbot\n 9. Deploy nginx.conf -> start Nginx\n10. Create + enable systemd service\n11. Verify: curl https://ineedq.com",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "setup.sh  —  Fresh Install\n──────────────────────────────────\nexport OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...\nexport DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-...\nexport LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET=...\n\n./setup.sh --email you@email.com\n\nScript steps:\n 1. DNS check (EC2 IP vs domain)\n 2. Validate API keys\n 3. Install: python3 pip3 node npm\n 4. Install: nginx certbot graphviz\n 5. pip install -r requirements.txt\n 6. npm install && npm run build\n 7. Write backend/.env (mode 600)\n 8. Issue SSL cert via certbot\n 9. Deploy nginx.conf -> start Nginx\n10. Create + enable systemd service\n11. Verify: curl https://ineedq.com",
      "version": 47,
      "versionNonce": 1794356837,
      "index": "d2",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "seed": 33,
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "rect_update",
      "x": 648.2426233685426,
      "y": 810.17814023802,
      "width": 345,
      "height": 310,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1d4ed8",
      "backgroundColor": "#eff6ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
