      "updated": 1772874926179,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Service Management & Monitoring\n──────────────────────────────────\nBackend:\n  systemctl status  trendpilot-backend\n  systemctl restart trendpilot-backend\n  systemctl stop    trendpilot-backend\n\nLive logs:\n  journalctl -u trendpilot-backend -f\n\nNginx:\n  sudo nginx -t          (test config)\n  sudo nginx -s reload   (zero downtime)\n  sudo nginx -s stop\n\nStop all services:\n  ./stop.sh\n\nVerify:\n  curl -I https://ineedq.com\n  curl https://ineedq.com/api/",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Service Management & Monitoring\n──────────────────────────────────\nBackend:\n  systemctl status  trendpilot-backend\n  systemctl restart trendpilot-backend\n  systemctl stop    trendpilot-backend\n\nLive logs:\n  journalctl -u trendpilot-backend -f\n\nNginx:\n  sudo nginx -t          (test config)\n  sudo nginx -s reload   (zero downtime)\n  sudo nginx -s stop\n\nStop all services:\n  ./stop.sh\n\nVerify:\n  curl -I https://ineedq.com\n  curl https://ineedq.com/api/",
      "version": 47,
      "versionNonce": 1578556389,
      "index": "d6",
      "isDeleted": false,
